data.description: Welcome to PARADISE! Magnificent 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, immaculate townhouse located in Aquabella community. This property features upgraded kitchen with SS appliances, upgraded patio, & a brand new gazebo. Energy efficient led lighting, water resistant laminate flooring, high end 1" glass railing on stairway. Smart home with wifi ac thermostat, tankless water heater, & Samsung washer & dryer. Cameras throughout the exterior of the home and over 1gb of high speed internet. Brand new window treatments throughout the home with blackout shades in the bedrooms. CORNER unit with magnificent views of the lake from many windows of the home. Gated and secured community 24/7 with 2 assigned parking spaces in front of the unit. Guest and overnight parking available.A must have! PRICE REDUCTION!
